WEBVTT

00:00:04.420 --> 00:00:06.630
Shah Rukh Khan: Have you ever been
saying something nasty

00:00:06.650 --> 00:00:08.680
about someone on a message

00:00:08.680 --> 00:00:13.080
and inadvertently sent the message 
to the person you were being mean to?

00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:18.430
Or posted something when angry 
and regretted it the next minute?

00:00:18.560 --> 00:00:22.400
Or tweeted about something 
that hurt someone,

00:00:22.480 --> 00:00:26.050
made them upset and then later
felt awful for doing that?

00:00:26.050 --> 00:00:27.720
Why did I do that?

